rate</strong> for short), a lightweight approach to package research data with their structured metadata, based on schema.org annotations in a formalized JSON-LD format that can be used independent of infrastructure to encourage FAIR sharing of reproducible datasets and analytical methods.</p>","doi":"10.5281/zenodo.3337883","grants":[{"acronym":"BioExcel-2","code":"823830","funder":{"acronyms":["EC"],"doi":"10.13039/501100000780","links":{"self":"https://zenodo.org/api/funders/10.13039/501100000780"},"name":"European Commission"},"links":{"self":"https://zenodo.org/api/grants/10.13039/501100000780::823830"},"program":"H2020","title":"BioExcel-2 Centre of Excellence for Computational Biomolecular Research"},{"acronym":"BioExcel","code":"675728","funder":{"acronyms":["EC"],"doi":"10.13039/501100000780","links":{"self":"https://zenodo.org/api/funders/10.13039/501100000780"},"name":"European Commission"},"links":{"self":"https://zenodo.org/api/grants/10.13039/501100000780::675728"},"program":"H2020","title":"Centre of Excellence for Biomolecular Research"}],"license":{"id":"CC-BY-4.0"},"publication_date":"2019-07-16","related_identifiers":[{"identifier":"10.5281/zenodo.3250687","relation":"isNewVersionOf","scheme":"doi"},{"identifier":"https://github.com/ResearchObject/ro2019/issues/3","relation":"isDocumentedBy","scheme":"url"},{"identifier":"10.5281/zenodo.3337882","relation":"isVersionOf","scheme":"doi"}],"relations":{"version":[{"count":1,"index":0,"is_last":true,"last_child":{"pid_type":"recid","pid_value":"3337883"},"parent":{"pid_type":"recid","pid_value":"3337882"}}]},"resource_type":{"subtype":"preprint","title":"Preprint","type":"publication"},"title":"RO-Crate, a lightweight approach to Research Object data packaging"},"owners":[4363],"revision":3,"stats":{"downloads":51.0,"unique_downloads":45.0,"unique_views":48.0,"version_downloads":51.0,"version_unique_downloads":45.0,"version_unique_views":48.0,"version_views":52.0,"version_volume":8905365.0,"views":52.